<lb n="0289b18"/><head type="no">No. 1261</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0289b19"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0289016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】卅帖策子第十六，【乙】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本</note><title>訶利帝母真言<note n="0289017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＝法【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0289017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經＝法【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0289017"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">法</rdg></app></title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0289b20"/>
<lb n="0289b21"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0289018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（開府…門））四十一字＝（（特進試鴻臚卿大廣善寺三藏沙門大廣智））十七字【宋】【元】【甲】，（（唐特進試鴻臚卿三藏沙門大廣智））十四字【明】【乙】</note><app n="0289018" word-count="41"><lem>開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國
<lb n="0289b22"/>公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒
<lb n="0289b23"/>正號大廣智大興善寺三藏沙門</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【甲】" resp="Taisho">特進試鴻臚卿大廣善寺三藏沙門大廣智</rdg><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">唐特進試鴻臚卿三藏沙門大廣智</rdg></app>
<lb n="0289b24"/>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0289b25"/><p>爾時訶利<note n="0289019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">帝＋（母）【乙】</note><app n="0289019"><lem>帝</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">帝母</rdg></app>藥叉女。在佛眾會從座而起。五
<lb n="0289b26"/>體投地禮佛雙足。而白佛言。我有心真言。
<lb n="0289b27"/><note n="0289020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">由＝猶【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0289020"><lem>由</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">猶</rdg></app>如真多摩尼寶能滿一切意願。為利益安
<lb n="0289b28"/>樂閻浮提諸善<note n="0289021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">男子及善女人＝女人及男女故【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0289021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">男子及善女人＝女人及男女故【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0289021"><lem>男子<note n="0289022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">及善女人＝善女人等及男女故&M062403;【乙】</note><app n="0289022"><lem>及善女人</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【乙】">善女人等及男女故</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">女人及男女故</rdg></app>。<note n="0289023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唯＝惟【三】【乙】</note><note n="0289023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯＝惟【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0289023"><lem>唯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">惟</rdg></app>願世尊
<lb n="0289b29"/>哀愍聽許。我今說之</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1261.0289c" n="0289c"/>
<lb n="0289c01"/><p>真言曰</p>
<lb n="0289c02"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0289024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唵＋（引一）夾註【三】【乙】</note><note n="0289024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唵＋（引一）夾註【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0289024"><lem>唵</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">唵<note place="inline">引一</note></rdg></app>弩弩麼<note place="inline">引</note>里迦<note place="inline">引</note>呬帝娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline"><note n="0289025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引＋（二）【三】【乙】</note><note n="0289025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引＋（二）【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0289025"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">引二</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0289c03"/><p>若有女人不宜男女。或在胎中墮落斷<note n="0289026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">緒＝敘【三】【甲】</note><note n="0289026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">緒＝敘【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0289026"><lem>緒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">敘</rdg></app>不
<lb n="0289c04"/>收。皆由四大<note n="0289027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＋（宜男女）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0289027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不＋（宜男女）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0289027"><lem>不</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">不宜男女</rdg></app>不能調適。或被鬼神作諸障
<lb n="0289c05"/>難。<note n="0289028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">或＝此【明】【乙】</note><app n="0289028"><lem>或</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">此</rdg></app>是宿業因緣不宜男女。應取白&CB00626;或一
<lb n="0289c06"/>肘或一<note n="0289029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00250;＝磔【三】【乙】</note><note n="0289029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00250;＝磔【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0289029"><lem>&CB00250;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">磔</rdg></app>手或長五寸<note n="0289030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（或）＋隨【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0289030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（或）＋隨【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0289030"><lem>隨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">或隨</rdg></app>意大小。畫訶利
<lb n="0289c07"/>帝母。作天女形<note n="0289031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">純＝像【三】【乙】</note><note n="0289031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">純＝像【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0289031"><lem>純</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">像</rdg></app>金色。身著天衣頭冠瓔
<lb n="0289c08"/>珞。坐<note n="0289032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">宣＝寶【三】＊</note><note n="0289032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">宣＝寶【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0289032"><lem>宣</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">寶</rdg></app>臺上垂下兩足。於垂足兩邊畫二孩
<lb n="0289c09"/>子。傍<app type="＊" source="0289032"><lem>宣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">寶</rdg></app>臺立。於二膝上各坐一孩子。以左
<lb n="0289c10"/><note n="0289033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔手〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0289033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔手〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0289033"><lem>手</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>懷中抱一孩子。於右手中持吉祥&CB00031;。畫師
<lb n="0289c11"/>應受八戒。其彩色中不用皮膠。畫像成已。淨
<lb n="0289c12"/>治一室嚴儀塗拭。以香<note n="0289034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">塗＝泥【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0289034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">塗＝泥【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0289034"><lem>塗</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">泥</rdg></app>作<note n="0289035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一〕－【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0289035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0289035"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>方壇。置像
<lb n="0289c13"/>壇中。以種種華散於壇上。復以甘脆飲食乳
<lb n="0289c14"/>糜酪飯及諸&CB00031;子閼伽香水。燒沈水香而<note n="0289036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔用〕－【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0289036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔用〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0289036"><lem>用</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0289c15"/>供養。像面向西持誦者面東。對像念誦每日
<lb n="0289c16"/>三時。時別誦一千遍。取月生五日起首。先誦
<lb n="0289c17"/><note n="0289037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">十＝千【元】【明】</note><app n="0289037"><lem>十</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">千</rdg></app>萬遍。然後對像前念誦。所求一切事皆悉
<lb n="0289c18"/>圓滿</p>
<lb n="0289c19"/><p>又法女人欲得男女者。月經後澡浴。取黃<note n="0289038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乳牛＝牛乳【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0289038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乳牛＝牛乳【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0289038"><lem>乳
<lb n="0289c20"/>牛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">牛乳</rdg></app>母子同色者。<note n="0289039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">搆＝&CB02206;【三】【乙】</note><note n="0289039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">搆＝&CB02206;【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0289039"><lem>搆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&CB02206;</rdg></app>乳一升置銀器中。以右手
<lb n="0289c21"/>無名指攪乳。誦真言加持一千八十遍。然後
<lb n="0289c22"/>取服。至<note n="0289040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">七＝五【三】【乙】</note><note n="0289040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">七＝五【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0289040"><lem>七</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">五</rdg></app>日內則得有胎</p>
<lb n="0289c23"/><p>又法欲令他人歡喜敬愛者。或飲食&CB00031;子或
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1261.0290a" n="0290a"/>
<lb n="0290a01"/>華或香。加持一百八遍。於真言句中加彼人
<lb n="0290a02"/>名。將與彼人則得歡喜<note n="0290001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">愛敬＝敬愛【宋】【明】【乙】，敬受【元】</note><note n="0290001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">愛敬＝敬愛【宋】【明】【乙】，＝敬受【元】</note><app n="0290001"><lem>愛敬</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">敬愛</rdg><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">敬受</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0290a03"/><p>又法若有人作留難口舌者。畫彼人形左&CB00560;
<lb n="0290a04"/>踏之。誦真言一千八十遍則得無難</p>
<lb n="0290a05"/><p>又法欲令一切人歡喜<note n="0290002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔者〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0290002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔者〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0290002"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。取牛黃末置銀器
<lb n="0290a06"/>中。准前以無名指攪誦真言加持一百八遍。
<lb n="0290a07"/>點於額上一切人見皆歡喜順伏</p>
<lb n="0290a08"/><p>又法若<note n="0290003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔得〕－【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0290003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔得〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0290003"><lem>得</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>新衣服。對像前加持一百八遍。然
<lb n="0290a09"/>後取著一切人見亦皆歡喜敬愛</p>
<lb n="0290a10"/><p>又法若有惡夢。誦真言一百八遍。則得惡夢
<lb n="0290a11"/>消除</p>
<lb n="0290a12"/><p>又法若月蝕時。取酥五兩置<note n="0290004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔金〕－【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0290004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔金〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0290004"><lem>金</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>器中。以金&CB00552;
<lb n="0290a13"/>攪。無<note n="0290005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔令〕－【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0290005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔令〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0290005"><lem>令</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>間斷念誦加持。乃至月&CB00230;得圓滿為
<lb n="0290a14"/>限。然後取一分供養訶利帝母。餘者漸喫。即
<lb n="0290a15"/>有胎孕所生男女聰慧福德　又法取牛膝根
<lb n="0290a16"/>作齒木。加持一百八遍嚼及揩齒。所出言詞
<lb n="0290a17"/>令人樂聞。意欲所求他人之事皆得隨意成
<lb n="0290a18"/>就　又法欲得壽命長遠者。取骨屢草嫩苗。
<lb n="0290a19"/>搵蘇蜜酪護摩七夜。夜別誦真言一千八<note n="0290006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遍一遍＝十遍【三】【乙】</note><note n="0290006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔遍〕－【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0290006"><lem>遍</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0290a20"/><note n="0290007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一遍一擲〕－【甲】</note><note n="0290007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一遍一擲〕－【甲】，一遍＝十遍【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0290007"><lem>一遍一擲</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">十遍一擲</rdg></app>火中則長壽</p>
<lb n="0290a21"/><p>又法欲得所為所作隨意成就者。每月<note n="0290008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔月〕－【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0290008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔月〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0290008"><lem>月</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>生
<lb n="0290a22"/>五日二十日。塗<note n="0290009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拭＝飾【三】【乙】</note><note n="0290009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">拭＝飾【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0290009"><lem>拭</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">飾</rdg></app>道場散華。種種飲食乳糜
<lb n="0290a23"/>酪飯。及諸&CB00031;子閼伽香水。燒沈香薰陸以用
<lb n="0290a24"/>供養。先供養一切如來文殊師利菩薩普賢
<lb n="0290a25"/>等一切菩薩。然後供養我訶利帝母。何以故。
<lb n="0290a26"/>我本藥叉女。如來<note n="0290010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">授＝受【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0290010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">授＝受【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0290010"><lem>授</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">受</rdg></app>與我三歸五戒菩提心
<lb n="0290a27"/>律儀戒。對諸十地菩薩故。是先供養諸佛菩
<lb n="0290a28"/>薩。供養已。對此像前誦一萬遍。所求事業皆
<lb n="0290a29"/>得滿足</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1261.0290b" n="0290b"/>
<lb n="0290b01"/><p>訶利帝母念誦法</p>
<lb n="0290b02"/><p>愛子心真言<note n="0290011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔曰〕－【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0290011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔曰〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0290011"><lem>曰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0290b03"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0290012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唵＋（引一）夾註【三】【乙】</note><note n="0290012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唵＋（引一）夾註【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0290012"><lem>唵</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">唵<note place="inline">引一</note></rdg></app>知<note place="inline">上</note>尾知<note place="inline">上</note>&CB00576;娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note><note n="0290013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訶＋（引二）夾註【三】【乙】</note><note n="0290013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訶＋（引二）夾註【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0290013"><lem>訶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">訶<note place="inline">引二</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0290b04"/><p>印合掌屈二大拇指入掌中。誦心真言供養
<lb n="0290b05"/>訖。於頂上放二大拇指即散去。請召發遣皆
<lb n="0290b06"/><note n="0290014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">放＝倣【三】【乙】</note><note n="0290014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">放＝倣【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0290014"><lem>放</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">倣</rdg></app>此印。以白檀香。橫量六指作童子形。具
<lb n="0290b07"/>足兩手各把&CB00031;子與人。頭上作三髻角子。於
<lb n="0290b08"/>閑<note n="0290015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">淨＝靜【三】【乙】</note><note n="0290015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">淨＝靜【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0290015"><lem>淨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">靜</rdg></app>處安置。誦真言<note n="0290016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（一）＋萬【乙】</note><app n="0290016"><lem>萬</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">一萬</rdg></app>遍。即現身問言。喚
<lb n="0290b09"/>我何事。隨心答之。取黃牛肉方寸。一加持一
<lb n="0290b10"/>燒日三時。滿四日得大自在隨意</p>
<lb n="0290b11"/><p>又法牛肉<note n="0290017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（和）＋安【乙】</note><app n="0290017"><lem>安</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">和安</rdg></app><note n="0290018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悉＝息【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0290018"><lem>悉</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">息</rdg></app>香為丸。月八日<note n="0290019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（日）＋三【乙】</note><app n="0290019"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">日三</rdg></app>時念誦。
<lb n="0290b12"/>燒上香<note n="0290020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一＋（千）【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0290020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一＋（千）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0290020"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">一千</rdg></app>八遍。至<note n="0290021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">十＋（四）&M062485;【乙】</note><sic n="0290021" corr="十四" resp="【乙】">十</sic>日已。夜半現大光相
<lb n="0290b13"/>得大神力。安<app type="＊" source="0290018"><lem>悉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">息</rdg></app>香為丸一加持一燒日三時。
<lb n="0290b14"/>時別一千八遍五日調伏一切人</p>
<lb n="0290b15"/><p>又法百草花一一加持散身上。得千人衣食</p>
<lb n="0290b16"/><p>又法日誦真言燒蘇合香七日。見地下金藏。
<lb n="0290b17"/><note n="0290022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝已【三】【甲】</note><note n="0290022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝已【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0290022"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">已</rdg></app>種種花&CB00031;飲食壇中供養。日日如是得一
<lb n="0290b18"/>切財寶</p>
<lb n="0290b19"/><p>又法安<note n="0290023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悉＝悉香【宋】【元】，息香【明】【乙】</note><note n="0290023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">悉＝悉香【宋】【元】，＝息香【明】【乙】</note><app n="0290023"><lem>悉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">悉香</rdg><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">息香</rdg></app>和乳粥。一加持一燒七日。日三時
<lb n="0290b20"/>時別一千八遍。現身共語<note n="0290024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">供＝任【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0290024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">供＝任【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0290024"><lem>供</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">任</rdg></app>意問</p>
<lb n="0290b21"/><p>又法被禁閉。誦一萬遍即解脫。治病加持菴
<lb n="0290b22"/>羅&CB00031;<note n="0290025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">芽＝葉【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0290025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">芽＝葉【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0290025"><lem>芽</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">葉</rdg></app>乳中漬燒加持。除一切病</p>
<lb n="0290b23"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead><title>訶利帝母<note n="0290026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＝真言法【三】【乙】，經＝法【甲】</note><note n="0290026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經＝真言法【宋】【元】【明】【乙】，經＝法【甲】</note><app n="0290026"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">真言法</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">法</rdg></app><note n="0290027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乙本冠註曰貞享四年二月十六挍點之了淨嚴四十九載，元祿十五年十一月二十五日以淨嚴大和尚御本再挍了尊教</note></title></jhead></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>